text: Jannine Weigel (; born 30 July 2000) is a singer and actress with Thai and German ancestry. Her work (music) on YouTube are what made her well-known. She was an artist under GMM Grammy and is now an independent artist in Germany. == Biography == Jannine Weigel was born in Steinfurt, Germany. She lived there until she was 10 years old, when her family moved to Thailand in July 2010. She has three brothers and sisters. She graduated from kindergarten at St. Martin, Steinfurt, Germany. She graduated from elementary school at Regen Boken Chulay Steinfurt city Germany, then studied for a bachelor's degree in advance, achievement card at Sukhothai Thammathirat Open University Faculty of Liberal Arts Department of English. Weigel graduated from junior high school at a distance education institution. == Career == Weigel appeared in the music video of Getsunova's Klai Khae Nai Khue Kla, which made her popular in 2012. Weigel started her YouTube channel in 2013, where she posts her covers and popular songs. She has many covers that went viral and have gained millions of views. == Discography == ===Studio albums=== * Genesis (September 17, 2015) * Deep End (July 6, 2017) == References == Category:Thai singers Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Thai actors Category:Protestants Category:Actors from North Rhine-Westphalia Category:German models
